tutorials.txt: Press <- or -> to move left or right.
Press the space bar to jump.
Hold longer for higher jumps. Land while holding space to auto-jump again.
Wall jump by pressing space again when hitting a wall.
It even works in the same direction!
Hold space and a direction key to keep jumping after a wall jump.
Press Shift and a direction key to dash. Pressing more than 2 keys cancels the dash. Regain dash upon landing.
Moving platforms start moving when stepped on. Some move automatically.
Jump off moving platforms while holding a direction key to carry the platform's speed.
Use jump pads for a boost upwards.
Temporary blocks disappear shortly after stepping on them.
Bubbles in the air restore your dash for another mid-air dash.
